info.name: cachecloud
info.description: (sohu tv)Redis Redis(StandaloneSentinelCluster)redis/(CacheCloud is a Redis cloud management platform. It supports Standalone, Sentinel, and Cluster architectures for Redis, effectively reducing large-scale Redis operation and maintenance costs, and improving resource management and utilization. The platform provides rapid construction/migration, operation and maintenance management, elastic scaling, statistical monitoring, client integration and access and other functions)
